eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu was there. Courtesy #DStv403 MUSINA, Limpopo - Government is waging a war against illegal immigrants coming into the country.
Over 200 Zimbabwean nationals have been arrested at the Beitbridge Border Post.
This is as the Home Affairs Department cracks down on illegal crossings between South Africa and Zimbabwe.
​​​​​​​eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu was there and shares more details in the video above.